<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Activity_method_arm  Entity: Activity_method  
   <express_ref linkend="activity_method:arm:Activity_method_arm.Activity_method"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Activity_method_arm.Activity_method">
An <b>Activity_method</b> specifies how an 
<express_ref linkend="Activity:arm:Activity_arm.Activity"/>
may be carried out,
There may be more than one method for producing the required result


<note> 
This definition may be the basis for activities or the solution for
requests for action (a  
<express_ref linkend="work_request:arm:Work_request_arm.Work_request"/>).
The identification of an <b>Activity_method</b> as a solution to a
<express_ref linkend="work_request:arm:Work_request_arm.Work_request"/>
is represented by the 
<express_ref
linkend="work_request:arm:Work_request_arm.Activity_method_assignment"/>
entity.
</note>
</ext_description>
